{"tid":1988460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報道：中國施壓歐盟刪疫情報告負面內容","createTime":"2020-04-25T08:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T08:35:26.000Z","uid":18569,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"12c40ab2372c7a5c2d76c7d7b230e25ae319bfff","tid":1988460,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:23:15.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】歐盟針對各地疫情假資訊發表監察報告，據報因中方施壓，刪減了批評中國的內容，對於有國家主張派國際專家到中國，就病毒源頭展開獨立調查，中方表明反對。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟對外事務部周五發表疫情假資訊監察報告，點名中國與俄羅斯針對歐盟與周邊國家，散播陰謀論，謀取自身利益。<br />\n<br />\n至少兩家傳媒報道，報告與最初版本內容與編排不同，淡化對中國的批評。<br />\n<br />\n例如原有版本首頁批評中國在全球散布假資訊，推卸疫情責任，挽回國際形象，正式發表的報告刪去以上內容。雖有批判中國，但認為「沒俄羅斯般猖獗」 。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述不同消息，報告原訂周二發表，部分內容當天早上被一個美國政治新聞網站搶先公布。<br />\n<br />\n中方高層得悉後，同日向歐盟駐華官員表明，如報告不經修訂就發布，嚴重不利雙方合作。知情人士又引述外交部前歐洲司楊曉光 ，稱公開報告將「觸怒中國」。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》報道，<span style=\"color: red;\">歐盟其後下達指示修改報告，不能過於側重批評中俄。決定據報引起內部不滿，至少一名研究員去信上級投訴，歐盟自我審查，討好中共。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n歐盟發言人否認受壓作修訂，強調報告如期發表。<br />\n<br />\n疫情漸趨穩定，不少國家開始追究中國責任，提出委派國際專家到當地，追查病毒源頭。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐英國使館公使陳雯質疑獨立調查要求帶有政治目的，只會分散抗疫資源與注意力，對各方沒有好處。又稱圍繞病毒源頭的謠言猶如「政治病毒」，可能較新型冠狀病毒更危險。<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/23822\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F23822&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=16fecbfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F23822&h=1f7fbe35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/23822</a>"},{"pid":"d02636b7f4a3bcb7e54dbeb5540b96d9e2071bab","tid":1988460,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:25:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">應該派軍隊保護專家<br />\n攻入蚑那夾硬調查</span></span>"},{"pid":"30c8becd11fe685c2724b5b83d24befa8e51f231","tid":1988460,"uid":182222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:25:22.000Z","msg":"老習係咪成日以為自己暗啞底做嘢冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fc4964d319e68342e3bcf9501d2adbf7e52f1b","tid":1988460,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30c8becd11fe685c2724b5b83d24befa8e51f231","tid":1988460,"uid":182222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:25:22.000Z","msg":"老習係咪成日以為自己暗啞底做嘢冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:27:08.000Z","msg":"知道又點<br />\n<br />\n歐盟、世衛、Youtube 全部都係中共嘅人<br />\n<br />\n屌2句之後繼續奶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60e776dd2b36305544b58abfe2df5ab8cafc89e","tid":1988460,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:29:43.000Z","msg":"仲有咁多人奶，世界承受咁大教訓都唔夠真係末日都得啦"},{"pid":"65f7324f9dec9109f86529892b7150d1365c47f5","tid":1988460,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:32:53.000Z","msg":"歐盟垃圾到咁<br />\n<br />\n一係你就咪撚發佈各地疫情報告啦<br />\n攞黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bb2698d7781f3b0ff1dee831e31832ee482d3a","tid":1988460,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:35:26.000Z","msg":"煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話畀鬼佬知支那連佢哋歐洲人嘅言論自由都要殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}